metadata.name: abcission #0001
metadata.description:
OneETHGame is a series of commemorative NFT to celebrate participants of OneETHGame, who have gathered to make a mark on the burgeoning Web 3.0 space along with 1ΞG DAO. Over the course of 8 weeks, participants will gain invaluable experience through buying and selling NFTs, making profit and taking losses along the way. We intend this game to be a collective experience where participants actively share information amongst themselves and learn from each other.

April 2022, 1ΞG DAO took its first steps as the inaugural OneETHGame started. A special thanks to the 50 OneETHGame participants who have made these first steps possible.

(The 1st OneETHGame is held from April 11th to June 5th, 2022)
